target_site "https://interactivebrokers.com"
login_required
enable_text_entry
wait 10000
explore_website_openai "Navigate to the Portfolio or Positions page. Locate the table containing stock symbols and the number of shares for each. Also, find the cash balance, which may be labeled as 'Net Cash', 'Total Cash', or 'Margin Balance'." 60
answer_query_text "List each stock holding with the number of shares. Also, report the cash balance or margin balance of the account. If no stocks are found, state that the portfolio is empty."
